{"tid":1309862,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[突發]警方白紙黑字將612定性為暴動 [暴動定性未收回]","createTime":"2019-07-12T11:35:23.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-13T05:02:33.000Z","uid":256620,"like":42,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":22,"replies":[{"pid":"bbb86930d9b68550798b9a67e1d936e13d81fc46","tid":1309862,"uid":256620,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-12T11:35:23.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/JoyRAjP.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FJoyRAjP.jpg&h=9b91dd3b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">暴動定性未撤銷<br />\n希望大家聚焦返五大訴求,唔好過份聚焦咁多支線</span></strong></span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">冇話唔比做連儂牆,各有各做冇問題<br />\n請記住五大訴求先係重點</span></span><br />\n<br />\n而家日日幾個post動員幾百人出去守連儂牆<br />\n咪由撚得佢哋拆，守黎托柒咩，再整過成本根本唔高<br />\n說好的拆一貼十呢？ 有人搗亂守得一日半日 班友第二日佢地咪又拆過 <br />\n我地去守 係去俾佢地玩 浪費精神體力, 放返重點去其他地方<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">唔撚該唔好再講到十萬火急 死人冧樓咁撚樣</span></span><br />\n拆完咪再貼 洗撚人守過夜咩,<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">唔好比人咁易帶風向,蒙古巨撚沙勇單野變左圍屌ANGELA YUEN<br />\n連儂牆變左人民鬥人民</span><br />\n唔該保持返獨立思考 <br />\n <span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\">唔割席唔篤灰</span></span><br />\n依家呢個關頭我地要贏最重要係雙普選<br />\n呢個先係真正治本既方法,<br />\n依家亦合情合理合法提出<br />\n係基本法寫到明架!!!<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\">不分化!</span></span></strong><br />\n五大訴求 <br />\n1.撤回<br />\n2.撤銷暴動定性<br />\n3.撤銷示威者控罪<br />\n4.追究警方濫權/成立獨立調查委員會<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">5.我要真普選</span></span>"},{"pid":"2badce2b82868d7fe0b0470068ce1cf7f1042f40","tid":1309862,"uid":256620,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-12T11:38:26.000Z","msg":"岑子杰：警將612定性暴動 將就警方當日行動提司法覆核<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.now.com/home/local/player?newsId=355157&amp;refer=\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fhome%2Flocal%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D355157%26refer%3D&d=QCZ5VELzTGqQZzcx9zTUyn%2B3Qbouwy6U%2BTFwRHAqvaY%3D&h=9e7f79be\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fhome%2Flocal%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D355157%26refer%3D&h=66e7f31a\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.now.com/home/local/player?newsId=355157&amp;refer=</a>"},{"pid":"19cc7545076cef67902a2dbe03efa546f1f696ed","tid":1309862,"uid":256620,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-12T11:42:39.000Z","msg":"五大訴求 <br />\n1.撤回<br />\n2.撤銷暴動定性<br />\n3.撤銷示威者控罪<br />\n4.追究警方濫權/成立獨立調查委員會<br />\n5.我要真普選"},{"pid":"fdf337f2313695757755c594ccfe17b1db78534b","tid":1309862,"uid":256620,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-12T11:42:53.000Z","msg":"PUSH<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f62e58b4b44abe028423889ddc4c9e1bf274e71a","tid":1309862,"uid":271470,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-12T11:43:00.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"f9277c84e8fe6425b0014f2fff93b43768cfc86c","tid":1309862,"uid":256620,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-12T11:44:29.000Z","msg":"聽日去上水"},{"pid":"c68ec700c51c994dcc99a6df8623a1b5f66a6cfc","tid":1309862,"uid":256620,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-12T11:47:21.000Z","msg":"兄弟爬山 五大訴求<br />\n<br />\n大家唔好真係淨係當口號<br />\n<br />\nD牆唔好落單, 亦唔好格硬守"},{"pid":"e01c20babbc34ba0db1728a6af1c82d1327f23e1","tid":1309862,"uid":256620,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-12T11:48:38.000Z","msg":"五大訴求 <br />\n1.撤回<br />\n2.撤銷暴動定性<br />\n3.撤銷示威者控罪<br />\n4.追究警方濫權/成立獨立調查委員會<br />\n5.我要真普選"},{"pid":"c62cda1ff706832731150bb13932ed82c3fa7aeb","tid":1309862,